::Justine looked at Sethra and Hipp solemnly::  But I know your visit has come to a close.  You need to get back to your people.  I know that feeling myself.  Is there anything you need before you leave?  Perhaps you would like one of Merlobo's ships to take you back in your lands in comfort this time? <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/BC.html BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Queen</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/30/00 4:15 pm)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/Hippolyte?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> the gift and evening</span><hr size=1> ::Hipp smiled at Justine..and then glanced quickly at the mare..then back to Justine and saluted her:: Efharisto/thanks....the mare is beautiful.  You have given me a wonderous gift.  Efaristo. ::Hipp looked back at the mare.. she looked forward to joining her into the herd back at Themiscrya.  She then watched Sethra with her puppy and smiled.  Then her eyes turned to Justine.::  You have given us enough gifts.  We shall journey back to our home as we came.  ::smiles..her pride as an amazon not wanting to depend on anyone to take them home.:: If it is endaksi/alright..we shall stay the night and rest again..then leave early ...very early in the morning. ::Hipp began walking back to the inn with the two women:: <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fed995><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/usethramaia.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Sethra Maia</A></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Registered User</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(8/31/00 7:29 am)</font><br>  