Your horses are ready for your departure.  There is a special saddlebag filled with food and drink for your trip.  And I have made sure that Captain Merlobo is shipping you a supply of this coffee you have become so fond of.  It should arrive even before you do.  And the mare and dog shall remind you both of your trip here.  And the love of our people for yours. <br>
Now, you best get some rest.  You have a long trip ahead of you come sunrise. <p></p><i></i></td></tr><tr bgcolor=#fbe5b4><td nowrap width=20% valign=top align=left><span class=title> <A HREF=http://pub11.ezboard.com/uhippolyte.showPublicProfile?language=EN>Hippolyte</A>&nbsp; <IMG SRC=http://hometown.aol.com/queenhippolyte/BC.html BORDER=0 WIDTH=10 HEIGHT=10></span><br> <span class=usertitle>Vasilissa</span><br>   <font color=#993300>(9/5/00 11:40 am)</font><br>    <BR><img src=http://facelink.com/Hippolyte?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60?flezbwidth=60&flezbheight=60 WIDTH=60 HEIGHT=60></td><td valign=top align=left class=m><span class=title> Re: Night</span><hr size=1> ::Hipp smiles at her new found friend::  Efharisto..thank you so much Justine. ::Hipp finishes her coffee and  then rises from her seat::  You have done so very much for us, and yes...we have enjoyed our stay here.  Just drop by Themiscrya when ever you can.  ::smiles:: We will show you a wild and fun time.  ::salutes her:: now.. I suppose I should see if I can get some rest tonight, before we leave.  Kalinihta psilos.  ::Hipp smiles softly:: in your language..goodnight friend ::she salutes Justine yet again..and then turns and goes back up the flight of stairs to her room.::: <p>@xxx}}::::::::::::::::::::>
